_sText:
This map is a defuse version of my previous map cs_complexo2, a "favela" map. I added normal maps to some textures and more detailing, and also an important lay-out change, an overpass crossing the map. Its quite a big map so its more fun to be played by many players. Deathmatch should be very fun. Nav file by Chizbone is included in the bsp.

I appreciate your feedback.
